<h1 id="highlights">Highlights</h1>

<h2 id="reapack---homepage">ReaPack - <a href="https://reapack.com">Homepage</a></h2>

<video poster="/assets/Reaper/Scripts/ReaPack.png" controls muted preload="none">
	<source src="/assets/Reaper/Scripts/ReaPack.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    Your browser does not support the video tag.
</video>
<div class="video-caption">ReaPack</div>

<p>ReaPack is a package manager for Reaper. It allows you to easily find, download <em>and</em> keep your scripts up to date. If you find that an update breaks something, then it’s easy to roll-back.</p>

<p>Most importantly: <a href="https://github.com/cfillion/reapack/wiki/Index-Format">it’s easy to get your owns contributions listed</a></p>

<h2 id="extremraym---homepage">ExtremRaym - <a href="https://www.extremraym.com/en/learn-reascript-reaper/">Homepage</a></h2>

<iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0Dwonn3Pe2Q" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>

<p>ExtremRaym has not only a number of <a href="http://www.extremraym.com/en/my-reaper-scripts/">awesome scripts</a>, but also has a website and video series documenting how to begin with ReaScript features yourself.</p>

<p><em>Highly Recommended</em></p>

<h2 id="heda-scripts---homepage">HeDa Scripts - <a href="https://reaper.hector-corcin.com">Homepage</a></h2>

<video poster="/assets/Reaper/Scripts/HeDa.png" controls muted preload="none">
	<source src="/assets/Reaper/Scripts/HeDa.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    Your browser does not support the video tag.
</video>
<div class="video-caption">HeDa Scripts</div>

<p>Hector Corcin has made a number of amazing scripts, along with their own download manager.</p>

<p>Personally I’m a huge fan of <a href="https://reaper.hector-corcin.com/app/track-inspector">Track Inspector</a> and <a href="https://reaper.hector-corcin.com/app/loudness-graph">Loudness Graph</a>.</p>

<p>Heda also has a VIP selection of scripts for donators with extended functionality and support.</p>

<h2 id="kawa---homepage">Kawa - <a href="http://kawa.works/reascripts">Homepage</a></h2>

<video poster="/assets/Reaper/Scripts/Kawa.png" controls muted preload="none">
	<source src="/assets/Reaper/Scripts/Kawa.mp4" type="video/mp4">
