<div class="video-caption">Just one Kawa jsfx</div>

<p>Kawa has a ridiculous number of scripts and jsfx. I don’t even know what to showcase here. <em>There’s</em> <strong>so much</strong>. Just go to the homepage and check it out.</p>

<p>Not only do the many of the jsfx have really cool GUIs, but they also sound fantastic. Many of the scripts do things that you may not even have thought was imaginable in a DAW. <strong>Go check it out!</strong></p>

<h2 id="mpl---homepage">MPL - <a href="https://forum.cockos.com/showthread.php?t=188335">Homepage</a></h2>

