<p>A modular synth in Reaper that’s fully extendable in via <a href="https://www.reaper.fm/sdk/js/js.php">JSFX</a>. ReaRack offers a selection of modules that can be linked together in creative ways to create a monster digital modular synth.</p>

<p>Since it can get quite complex, it includes some example projects to show how things can be done.</p>

<h2 id="sonic-anomaly---homepage">Sonic Anomaly - <a href="http://sonic.supermaailma.net/plugins">Homepage</a></h2>

