    Your browser does not support the video tag.
</video>
<div class="video-caption">Advanced Tempo Tool</div>

<p>Advanced Tempo Tool allows you to create complex tempo maps with ease. Often the process of changing tempos/time signatures can be a tedious hair-pulling experience, but ATT lets you keep that hair.</p>

<p>Creating complex time signature changes and tempo changes (which Reaper optionally will stretch item times or stretch the items themselves to) becomes a fun task.</p>

<h2 id="reanoir---thread">ReaNoir - <a href="https://forums.cockos.com/showpost.php?p=1820107&amp;postcount=1">Thread</a></h2>

