<p>Colours. Colours everywhere! Organize your projects in style using a variety of stylized palletes of your own design or choosing.</p>

<p>ReaNoire makes the colour-coding of your projects easy.</p>

<h2 id="track-item-manipulation---thread">Track-Item Manipulation - <a href="https://forum.cockos.com/showthread.php?t=194414">Thread</a></h2>

<video poster="/assets/Reaper/Scripts/TrackItemName.png" controls muted preload="none">
