<p>Renaming tracks is time consuming. Renaming items is a horrifying experience. What if you could easily manipulate the names of tracks and items without sacrificing your lifespan?</p>

<p>Track/Item Manipulation let’s you do that. Select your tracks <em>or</em> items and easily batch adjust the naming to what you need.</p>

<h2 id="track-lists---thread">Track lists - <a href="https://forum.cockos.com/showthread.php?t=176578">Thread</a></h2>

<video poster="/assets/Reaper/Scripts/TrackList.png" controls muted preload="none">
