<h1 id="donate">Donate!!</h1>

<p>This post took dozens of hours to research, screencap, write and edit, <strong>but If you appreciate the information presented then please donate to the script authors!</strong></p>

<p>These scripts can take hundreds of hours of a person’s free time. Many of them are written simply because someone had a problem on the forum, or mentioned some lacking functionality.</p>

<p>If you have the spare money and you find a script enjoyable then please look to see if the author accepts donations.</p>

<p>If not, then just send them a thanks. They’d love to know that their effort is appreciated.</p>

